QUESTION: Click on this code (you might have to double click or triple click it idk) but once it highlights copy the code and paste it somewhere safe where you can copy it from there again, then you can load your game by pasting it back here in "load game" type yes in the answer box when you are sure you have the code.

MESSAGE: Please Type "Yes" if you have the code.

QUESTION: Paste your code here to load your game, you can also type "delete" to erase all data, or "fullsave" to get the whole save.  Once you submit your code/answer and click the green flag to run the game again.  Make sure you have the right code as your load won't work if it's not the right code.

MESSAGE: INVALID CODE!

Freddy Fazbear: He approaches your office from the Left Hallway.  When he is at the closest point, shut the Left Door on him to send him away.  How fast he moves depends on the Temperature.  (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

Bonnie: Check the figurine on the desk.  If it's Bonnie, do NOT check Pirates Cove! If you do Bonnie will jumpscare you and block your cameras for a bit.  Remember Foxy cannot move when Bonnie is on the table.  (Can be eliminated with the Death Coin)

Chica: She spends her time in The Kitchen.  She mainly listens to the music, but sometimes she can get tired of the same music playing so loud! If she is gone then quickly change the music, changing it when she is in The Kitchen will make her leave completely to attack you! Having the Global Music Box on will keep her happy.

Foxy: Check the figurine on the desk.  If it's Foxy, check on the Pirates Cove camera to hold him back! If you aren't checking enough, Foxy will start moving out of Pirates Cove and when he leaves, he will enter your office piece by piece! eventually leading to a jumpscare.  (Can be eliminated with the Death Coin)

Toy Freddy: He sits in the Parts/Service room playing a videogame called "Five Nights With Mr Hugs".  You must check on Toy Freddy and shut the appropriate door on the screen to prevent Mr Hugs from jumpscaring him, otherwise Toy Freddy will try to jumpscare you too! (Can be eliminated with the Death Coin)
Toy Bonnie: Put on the mask when he is entering the office to send him away!
Toy Chica: Put on the Freddy Mask when she is entering the office to send her away!

Mangle: They try to get into your office with the Air Vents, shut the appropriate Vent Snare or close the Middle Vent Door when using the camera to stop them from getting into the office.  They will enter otherwise! and will probably jumpscare you soon after that.  (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

BB: When he appears at the Right Vent Door, close it to send him away.  Otherwise using your camera will most likely let him into your office and he will disable your flashlight! (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

JJ: When she appears at the Right Vent Door, close it to send her away.  Otherwise using your camera will most likely let her into your office and she will disable all of your door controls! (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

Withered Chica: She approaches to your office through the Air Vents, shut the appropriate Vent Snare or the Middle Vent Door before she gets in to send her away.  If she gets through she will get stuck in the vent! blocking your Middle Vent Door from closing and attempting to jumpscare you! (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)
Withered Bonnie: When you have your camera active, Withered Bonnie may appear in your office flickering the screen! put the Freddy mask on quick to avoid his jumpscare!

Marionette: Letting the Music Box completely wound down will cause it to flee off to get you! wind the box back up either by holding in the button at CAM 4, or by using the Global Music Box.  (Can be eliminated with the Death Coin)
Golden Freddy: When he is in the office, put on the Freddy Mask to make him disappear.  You have a short time when you bring the camera down to put the mask on before he jumpscares you!

Springtrap: He approaches your office with the Air Vents.  he can't be stopped with the Vent Snare, but before he enters your office you will see his face in the vent! close your Middle Vent Door then to send him back to the start.  (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

Phantom Mangle: When they appear when you put up your camera, close it or change the system to send them away.  If you are too slow, they will pull your camera down, appear in your office, and increase the noise meter!

Phantom Freddy: He slowly fades in inside your office, flash your light in the office to make him fade away.  Heat causes him to appear faster and when he fully appears, he will jumpscare you giving an opportunity for vent animatronics to come in if your Middle Vent Door is Open!

Phantom BB: If he appears when you put up your camera, close it change the cam or system to send him away.  If you are too slow, he will jumpscare you which fortunately will not lead to a game over, but your camera will be pulled down! and you may not be able to see for a bit which could catch you off guard to a lethal office Animatronic!

Nightmare Freddy: His Freddles can appear in your office when you have your camera up, use the flashlight to get rid of them before all of them appear and spawn Nightmare Freddy! Which will lead to a game over.

Nightmare Bonnie: Some point during the night, he will appear in The Right Hall.  You have a short time to be able to look at other cameras or systems before he can attack! Buy his plushie at the Prize Corner to prevent him from jumpsxaring you.  The Right Door can't stop him either!

Nightmare Fredbear: He can show up when your camera is up, you will hear his laugh and see his eyes right outside the Left Door! Close the Left Door to send him away.  (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

Nightmare: He can show up when your camera is up, you will hear his laugh and see his eyes right outside the Right Door! Close the Right Door to send him away.  (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

Jack O' Chica: When the Temperature gets high, she will start to appear at both hallways and will attack you if she fully fades in! Shut both Left and Right Doors to make her disappear from both hallways.  Careful! She will be unstoppable by the doors if the office is 100 Degrees or more.

Nightmare Mangle: Some point during the night, they will appear in The Right Hall.  You have a short time to be able to look at other cameras or systems before they can attack! Buy their plushie at the Prize Corner to prevent them from jumpscaring you.  The Right Door can't stop them either!
Nightmarionne: He will fade in when your mouse cursor is touching him, make sure not to make him fully appear! otherwise it's game over.

Nightmare BB: Every time you use your camera, make sure to keep an eye on Nightmare BB when you put your camera down again! If he is standing up, flash your light at him to prevent him from attacking when you use the camera again.  Watch out though! If he isn't standing up and you point your flashlight at him its also game over!

Old Man Consequences: A minigame will apear on screen, press "C" on the mark to catch the fish.  If you don't do this in time, you will be forced out of your camera view! and your camera will be locked for a certain amount of time.

Circus Baby; Some point during the night, she will appear in The Right Hall.  You have a short time to be able to look at other cameras or systems before she can attack! Buy their plushie at the Prize Corner to prevent her from jumpsxaring you.  The Right Door can't stop her either!

Ballora: She will try to attack you every now and then, when she does you will hear her music from the left or right and you only have a short amount of time to shut the appropriate door! otherwise game over.  (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

Funtime Foxy: At Funtime Cove, a time will be displayed telling you when Funtime Foxy's show starts.  They really want you to be there! so study the hour mark carefully and make sure you are looking at Funtime Cove otherwise you are most likely going to be jumpscared by Funtime Foxy.  (Can be eliminated with the Death Coin)

Ennard: He travels through the Air Vents, but it's hard too see where he is! However he is immune to the Vent Snare and when he gets to the end of the vent you will hear loud squeaky metal, close the Middle Vent Door then so he won't jumpscare you.  (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

Trash And The Gang: They are just a joke character who will try to jumpscare you at random times, you'll get used to it though! However Mr Can Do can sometimes block one of your cams a little bit so be wary of that in case it screws you over in the long run.
Helpy: He may show up if you use your camera! Quickly check if he's in the office, and if he is, click on him before he uses his airhorn which will increase your noise meter.
Happy Frog: She approaches to your office through the Air Ducts, usually going for the open duct.  Use the Audio Lure to keep her in place.  She is immune to The Heater!
Mr Hippo: He approaches to your office through the Air Ducts, usually going for the open duct.  Use the Audio Lure to keep him in place.  The Heater can also push him back every now and again too!

Pig Patch: He approaches to your office through the Air Ducts, usually going for the open duct.  Use the Audio Lure to make sure he doesn't reach the opening.  The Heater can also push him back to the start every now and again too!
Nedd Bear: He approaches to your office through the Air Ducts, usually going for the open duct.  He is only fooled by the Audio Lure 50% of the time! But The Heater can effectively push him back!

Orville Elephant: He approaches to your office through the Air Ducts, usually going for the open duct.  Unfortunately he's rarely fooled by the Audio Lure, but he can be pushed back very quickly with The Heater!

Rockstar Freddy: He can activate during the night and if he does, he will ask for 5 Fazcoins.  Paying him the 5 Fazcoins will deactivate him again, or you could try to malfunction him with The Heater.  If he stays active for too long, you will be jumpscared!

Rockstar Bonnie: When your camera is up there is a chance Rockstar Bonnie will come in to your office! His Guitar will be located then in one of the cameras.  Click on it to send him away, and before it is too late! (Can be eliminated with the Death Coin)

Rockstar Chica: She hates wet floor signs, and will always try to enter your office by the door that doesn't have the sign in place! Move the sign to her side to send her away.  You can also Camera Stall her, or just close the door she's at to prevent her from attacking every time you use your camera!

Rockstar Foxy: Remember that bird? and if you click on it Rockstar Foxy offers you help? well not all the time, sometimes Rockstar Foxy will actually jumpscare you! So think about if you want to click on that bird.  The higher Rockstar Foxy's A.I, the higher the chance he will jumpscare you when you click the bird.

Music Man: He will be triggered if you make too much noise, and you will hear his cymbals.  Overtime the cymbals will clash faster and faster until Music Man decides to jumpscare you! Make sure to keep him calm and keep your noise meter as low as possible.
El Chip: He's non lethal, but will block your screen with his ads! Close them by clicking the skip button or with the "E" key.
Funtime Chica: She's non lethal, but will try to distract you with her and the camera flashes! there is nothing you can do but it will only block your screen a bit for a short time.

Molten Freddy: He climbs through the Air Ducts to get to your office, and he is immune to the Vent Snare! Listen out for his laugh and the shut the Middle Vent Door so he can't get in and jumpscare you.  (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

Scrap Baby: She is only able to attack once a night.  She can appear in your office when your camera is up but when she does show up, keep an eye out for her looking up! You have a controlled shock on your desk, click on it to get rid of her otherwise using your camera will make it game over.

Afton: He will only attack one per night, but when he shows up you must react fast! You will hear loud clanging in the Right Vent, shut the Right Vent Door quickly! You have very little time to react before he gets you! (You are given a Fazcoin when you counter this character)

Lefty: They are very sensitive to heat and noise, having a high temperature or a high noise meter will cause them to activate and eventually they will be able to attack you while not watching them on the camera! however, you can use Global Music Box to calm them down again.  (Can be eliminated with the Death Coin)

Phone Guy: He will phone every now and again. A Mute Call button will show on screen and you must click it before it disappears! Otherwise the call will stay on for a long time, and will cause the noise meter to increase!
